place.name: CHAPEL ST LEONARDS
place.gazetteerText: CHAPEL-MUMBY, a hamlet in Mumby parish, Lincoln; on the coast, 5½ miles ESE of Alford. Pop., 316. (In 1870-72, John Marius Wilson's Imperial Gazetteer of England and Wales)
